name: spo-import-csv-data-to-existing-sharepoint-list
title: Import CSV to an existing SharePoint List
shortDescription: This script shows how to import a CSV to an existing SharePoint list without explicitly enumerating all list fields
longDescription: This script shows how to import a CSV to a SharePoint list  . Main idea here is use PnP-AddListItem without needing to enumerate each and every field in the code .

references.name: Want to learn more about PnP PowerShell and the cmdlets
references.description: Check out the PnP PowerShell site to get started and for the reference to the cmdlets.
